<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمَكَّةُ المُكَرَّمَة * مَدِينَةٌ مُعَظَّمَة<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَمَدْحُهَا يُحِبُّ كُلُّ شَاعِرٍ أَنْ يَنْظِمَه<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قُلُوبُنَا بِحُبِّهَا * مَلِيئَةٌ وَمُفْعَمَة<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَحَوْلَ بَيْتِهَا الحَرَامِ رُوحُنَا مُحَوِّمَة<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِقَلَم / يَاسِر الحَمَدَاني<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c1">" المِيكْرُوبَاظ بَاظ مِنْ زَمَان، وِاللِّي كَان كَان "</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>إِنَّا لَنَحْلُمُ بِالخَلاَصْ * مِنْ مُشْكِلاَتِ المِيكْرُوبَاصْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>نَضْطَرُّ نَرْكَبَهُ لأَنَّا مَا لَنَا عَنهُ مَنَاصْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>